{"id":502,"date":"2015-01-13T14:30:40","date_gmt":"2015-01-13T14:30:40","slug":"into-the-app-vol-2","title":"Into the app &#8211; vol 2","content":"<p>Yo folks, you should have received a notification today. Something like this:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-533 size-full\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/notification.jpg\" alt=\"notification\" width=\"1600\" height=\"875\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/notification.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yep it&#8217;s kinda party time, BIG update has been released. There are some cool perks inside but let&#8217;s focus here on a major change: <strong>the uploading process!</strong></p>\n<p>1st step hasn&#8217;t changed: you got a sick content you wanna show it so you click on that little (magic!) sign &#8216;+&#8217; at the bottom of the screen and then on the camera icon, you choose your filter and =&gt; you&#8217;re at that page:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-534\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg\" alt=\"app screen upload\" width=\"1026\" height=\"1026\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/app-screen-upload.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1026px) 100vw, 1026px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p>Here is the news: now you&#8217;re able to upload right away a content without a spot attached to it.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Which means that if you click on the &#8216;upload&#8217; button <strong>BANG</strong> your video / pic is instantaneously right up in the air with no spot. Why&#8217;s that?</p>\n<p>While some people love the fact to map their city and create some spots we&#8217;ve to admit that skateboarding is way way wilder than that. For ex. look at those next 2 pics. First one by <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" title=\"No Wax by Aldeanda\" href=\"http://skatekrak.com/shot/L0HOUFaGD1\" target=\"_blank\">Aldeanda</a></strong></span>; second one by <strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" title=\"Skatetime by Felix\" href=\"http://skatekrak.com/shot/3YJ5jLD3XD\" target=\"_blank\">Felix</a></span></strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://skatekrak.com/shot/L0HOUFaGD1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-506 size-medium\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/nowax.jpg\" alt=\"nowax\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/nowax.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/nowax.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/nowax.jpg 292w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/nowax.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>  <a href=\"http://skatekrak.com/shot/3YJ5jLD3XD\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-507 size-medium\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hand.jpg\" alt=\"hand\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/hand.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/hand.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/hand.jpg 292w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/hand.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Our question has been: <strong>does it make sense to attach a specific spot to them?</strong> It&#8217;s skateboarding related for sure which means it makes sense to have them in the app. But because it&#8217;s more <em>artistic</em> and/or <em>general</em>, you don&#8217;t necessarily want to attach a spot to them.</p>\n<p>Our solution has been simple: <strong>let&#8217;s people choose</strong>. Now each time you wanna upload some content in the app, you have the choice: map it or not.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">If you don&#8217;t care about the spot</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s damn simple: you click on the &#8216;upload&#8217; button and it&#8217;s up.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">If you care about the spot</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;map&#8217; button and here you are:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-540\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1326\" height=\"1326\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/type-a-name-2.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1326px) 100vw, 1326px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2 ways now:<br />\n&#8211; if the spot is on the list (ie it already has been created by someone), you just need to click on it<br />\n&#8211; if not you have this little sentence at the end of the list (like in the following screenshot), click on it</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-539\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1022\" height=\"1022\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/type-a-name.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1022px) 100vw, 1022px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Then you&#8217;ll get a pop up like the following one, it will send us a direct message and we&#8217;ll be able to create ourselves the spot. Give us as many details as possible to make the process easier. Then we promise to do it in the next few hours max (yep we don&#8217;t sleep a lot, we&#8217;ve a hell of a passion for this!).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;uo=4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-538\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1262\" height=\"1262\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/spot-info1.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1262px) 100vw, 1262px\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">If you care about the spot and YOU wanna create it yourself</span></strong></span> (yep we love surprises, so it&#8217;s possible)</p>\n<p>In this case: krak in first! Which means that before uploading your content, when you click on the button &#8216;+&#8217; at the bottom of the screen, click on the &#8216;pin&#8217; icon (versus the camera one). You&#8217;ll get that page:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-536\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg\" alt=\"KRAK IN\" width=\"1297\" height=\"1297\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/KRAK-IN.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1297px) 100vw, 1297px\" /></a></p>\n<p>And from there, if you click on the sentence at the end of the list, you&#8217;ll get that:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-535\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg\" alt=\"new spot\" width=\"1259\" height=\"1259\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 1600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_150/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_651/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 651w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_994/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 994w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_292/mag/uploads/new-spot.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1259px) 100vw, 1259px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Here you&#8217;re able to create your spot as usual. And then you can upload your content and attach the spot you just created to it.</p>\n<p>Well we&#8217;re dying to discuss w/ you if you have any feedback / questions so please, feel free to reach us.<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> <a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" title=\"Instagram Krak\" href=\"http://instagram.com/skate_krak\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a></span>, <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" title=\"Twitter Krak\" href=\"http://twitter.com/skatekrak\" target=\"_blank\">twitter</a></span>, mail whatever you want (mine is: k@skatekrak.com).</p>\n<p>Cheers folks, and keep on pushin&#8217;</p>\n","author":"kev","categories":["appguide"],"tags":["app-store","guide","krak-app","krak-in","skateboarding-app","spots","tips","update"],"featuredImages":[{"file":"update.jpg","width":1100,"height":733,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","source_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/update.jpg"}],"video":""}